Package org.openlca.ecospold.io

Class DataSet

java.lang.Object
org.openlca.ecospold.io.DataSet
public class DataSet extends Object
An adapter class for EcoSpold 01 data sets which provides an easy access to internal elements of data sets and ensures that 'path' elements are created when such internal elements are set.
